description:
On today’s show, Emily is joined by Scheana Shay – host of the podcast Scheananigans with Scheana Shay and star of the Bravo show Vanderpump Rules & they’re talking about being single, masturbation, & so much more.

 

They discuss why freezing your eggs may be something to you want to consider and how being single for awhile – after jumping from relationship to relationship – can help you realize what you actually need. Plus Emily gives advice on making sex compromises – and actually sticking to them and how to get past the bedroom panic and into pleasure.
